# Authoritative for hidden-master.demo. — exists to surface the
# self-only stealth NS detection from spec 007. The interesting bit
# is in the auth zone file: it advertises THREE NSes for the zone,
# but the parent (root) referral lists only TWO of them. The third
# (`hidden-primary.hidden-master.demo.`) is the stealth NS — present
# in the auth's NS RR set but absent from the parent's referral. Its
# A record is intentionally absent from every reachable source, so
# the active reachability probe (FR-010) reads 0 — modeling a
# "leaked listing" rather than a working hidden master.

hidden-master.demo. {
    file /zones/hidden-master.demo.zone
    log
    errors
}
